r />\n同埋，你真係信大陸淨係武漢出事？唔會由武漢spread去其他省份？<br />\n<br />\n為求自保，出街帶口罩啦<br />\n<br />\n要一人行一步，防止社區爆發呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFrgXW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFrgXW1.png&h=6510022b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZaEUdw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZaEUdw.png&h=9c751baa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEvJBhZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEvJBhZ.png&h=95690e68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X59uwRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX59uwRt.png&h=40f9ad0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08TZUer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08TZUer.png&h=dc5f3de9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOtZUes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOtZUes.png&h=eb37c162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oN3aHmIfpbw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoN3aHmIfpbw&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=6ca4318f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oN3aHmIfpbw</a>"},{"pid":"1d3fabce8d194bda8f58c86100485db1ea1f9175","tid":1811793,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"香港政府班太監求老細恩賜啲病毒添啦"},{"pid":"bada06bf452ca45a1ec67369f6c62320aff01960","tid":1811793,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1415ee1bf88ee166fd9f8f9d666ecba259ba59e4","tid":1811793,"uid":175346,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e9e625923dcd12af4837a7142917c8dd640a0965","tid":1811793,"ui